 TC #3

 Summary: Create spare part.

 Pre-conditions:
   1. Go to http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com.
   2. Enter valid values in field "Email" .
   3. Enter valid values in field  "Password".
   4. Click the button "Вход".

 Steps to reproduce:
   1. In left panel choice "Словари" => "Запчасти".
   2. Click  button "+".
   3. In field "Spare name" enter valid name.
   4. In field "Тип детали"  in pop-up menu choice any detail.
   5. Click the button "Создать".

  Expected result:
    Spare part created.

   ____________________________________________________________________________________________


