    TC #5

     Summary: Сreate a deal.

     Pre-conditions:
         1. Go to http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com.
         2. Enter valid values in field "Email" .
         3. Enter valid values in field  "Password".
         4. Click the button "Вход".

    Steps to reproduce:
      1. In left panel choice "Сделка" .
      2. Click  button "+".
      3. Enter in field "Deal date" valid values .
      4. In pop up menu field "Тип сделки" choice any deal.
      5. In pop up menu field "Покупатель" choice any name.
      6. In pop up menu field "Поставщик" choice any name.
      5. Click the button "Создать".

     Expected result:
      Deal  created.